title: AD Main | Smurfing | LF Female Support Player
body:

Prefer a Jana / Lulu player. Smurfing this account to Plat. Must have discord and be tilt-free. 
If I'm going to be carrying someone anyways I'd rather queue with you and not have an auto-fill support. 


Cheers.
